      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with some fading clear coat on the hood and a few minor door dings, while the interior has noticeable wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it starts and runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. It is a solid, functional car that has been used regularly and priced according to its current state.",
