    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she\u2019s a total beauty! This car has been babied since day one, always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every weekend. It honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Come see it for yourself\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
